- legacy API quarantine/removal
- salvage refactors
- CLI redesign beyond what is needed for clear error reporting

---------------------------------------------------------------------

Implementation guidance

- Detect duplicates once, against the final logical path set.
- Fail before writing archive/index structures.
- Prefer explicit erroring over clever renaming.
- Keep logic simple and deterministic.

